I spend the day your way

363
00:22:50,900 --> 00:22:57,470
Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley

364
00:22:57,470 --> 00:23:00,130
In and around the lake

365
00:23:01,180 --> 00:23:05,290
Mountains come out of the sky and they stand there

366
00:23:08,260 --> 00:23:12,050
One mile over we'll be there and we'll see you

367
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:18,480
Ten true summers we'll be there and laughing too

368
00:23:21,170 --> 00:23:26,500
Twenty four before my love you'll see I'll be there with you

369
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:31,560
これが吸血鬼
这就是吸血鬼吗

370
00:23:31,560 --> 00:23:33,920
解体してやる　ストレイツォ
我要把你给肢解了 史特雷兹

371
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:36,770
我がドイツの医学　薬学は世界一
我大德意志的医学药学乃世界第一

372
00:23:36,770 --> 00:23:38,550
君はなにもわかっちゃいないのだ
你什么都不明白

373
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:40,600
地獄で詫びろ
在地狱里谢罪吧

374
